{"tid":1158334,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"真正球隊主人 曼聯公布新季戰衣 普巴擔正宣傳","createTime":"2019-05-17T01:39:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T04:48:13.000Z","uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3312bf94d075623962e8ad00a860ac2bd0eb3f0e","tid":1158334,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T01:39:30.000Z","msg":"曼聯昨公布新季主場球衣，盛傳有意離隊轉投皇家馬德里的保羅普巴，出現在宣傳照正中位置。球衣設計紀念1999年3冠王成就，如衫袖分別印有當年歐聯決賽反勝的兩個補時入球時間。然而，曼聯今季英超僅排第6，下季需穿這球衣出戰歐霸盃。<br />\n<br />\n隨着球季結束，英超轉會窗昨早開啟，8月9日在開季前關閉。在下月11日國際足協轉會系統運作前，交易只可涉及英格蘭聯賽球員。傳曼聯首個收購，將以1000萬鎊（約1億港元）羅致英冠史雲斯翼鋒丹尼爾占士。<br />\n<br />\n英軍點兵戰歐國聯 卡尼帶傷入選<br />\n<br />\n另外，英格蘭隊公布下月初歐洲國家聯賽4強對荷蘭的27人初選名單，仍在養傷的熱刺射手哈利卡尼依舊入選。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.standard.co.uk/s3fs-public/thumbnails/image/2019/05/15/19/manutdnewkit18.jpg?width=1000&amp;height=614&amp;fit=bounds&amp;format=pjpg&amp;auto=webp&amp;quality=70&amp;crop=16:9,offset-y0.5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.standard.co.uk%2Fs3fs-public%2Fthumbnails%2Fimage%2F2019%2F05%2F15%2F19%2Fmanutdnewkit18.jpg%3Fwidth%3D1000%26height%3D614%26fit%3Dbounds%26format%3Dpjpg%26auto%3Dwebp%26quality%3D70%26crop%3D16%3A9%2Coffset-y0.5&h=0e43024b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9fb43ea7874365738b4292e672b2cad53ac3058","tid":1158334,"uid":3358,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T01:49:54.000Z","msg":"然而，曼聯今季英超僅排第6，下季需穿這球衣出戰歐霸盃。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n寫稿個個應該係猁"},{"pid":"bb1a0474a004fcec872f2e77e468a685585048c9","tid":1158334,"uid":34468,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"c9fb43ea7874365738b4292e672b2cad53ac3058","tid":1158334,"uid":3358,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T01:49:54.000Z","msg":"然而，曼聯今季英超僅排第6，下季需穿這球衣出戰歐霸盃。<img s